title: Updated the 2020 Feb updates of Android 10 and the Pixel Imprint scanner was not work.
content:
Just updated the 2020 Feb updates of Android 10, and use the application that need Pixel Imprint to unlock the application, and it always said there is dust on the scanner, please clean it.
I just clean and not work. and then I removed the old fingerprint and tried to add a new one. The Pixel Imprint UI can not add the new one (always on please use finger to touch scanner back of phone), no vibration sense. Please help me to fix that.
category: Setting up and Personalizing your Device, Google Pixel 3 XL
